# ------
49. Iota
# ------

Within a constant declaration, the predeclared identifier iota represents successive untyped
integer constants. It is reset to 0 whenever the reserved word const appears in the source. It can be used to construct a set of related constants:

code: https://play.golang.org/p/_cSkz_b28t
code: https://play.golang.org/p/YOabnTj5OI
code: https://play.golang.org/p/c5SmcFzzBM

